quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Nena: “Zavumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuti gulu la majini lidamvera chivumbulutso cha Mulungu ndipo lidati: Ndithudi ife tamva mawu odabwitsa.”"
  72,2,“Amene apereka dongosolo la kunjira yoyenera ndipo ife takhulupirira zonse zimene zinali kunenedwa ndipo ife sitidzalambira wina aliyense kupatula Ambuye wathu.”
  72,3,‘Ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wathu. Iye sadakwatire kapena kubereka ana
  72,4,‘Ndipo kuti anthu opusa amene ali pakati pathu akhala ali kumanenera Mulungu zinthu zonyasa kwambiri
  72,5,"‘Ndipo, ndithudi, ife timaganiza kuti kulibe munthu kapena majini amene angakanene chinthu chabodza chokhudza Mulungu"
  72,6,"‘Ndipo, ndithudi, padali anthu pakati pa mtundu wa anthu amene amapeza chitetezo kuchokera kwa anthu a mtundu wa majinn. Koma iwo adangoonjezera kuchita zoipa ndi kusakhulupilira"
  72,7,"‘Ndipo iwo adayamba kuganiza monga momwe inu mumaganizira, kuti Mulungu sadzadzutsa wina aliyense"
  72,8,‘Ndipo ife tidafuna kupita kuthambo la pamwamba zedi ndipo tidaona kuti linali lodzadzidwa ndi ogwira ntchito a mphamvu ndi nyenyezi za moto
  72,9,"‘Ndithudi ife tinali Al Jinn\t623 kukhala m’menemo kumvetsera koma amene azimvetsera tsopano, adzapeza malawi a moto uli kumudikira"
  72,10,‘Ife sitidziwa ngati akuwafunira mavuto anthu awo amene ali padziko lapansi kapena kuti Ambuye wawo ali ndi cholinga choti awatsogolere
  72,11,‘Alipo ena pakati pathu amene ndi angwiro pamene ena ndi ochimwa. Ife ndife magulu otsatira njira zosiyanasiyana
  72,12,‘Ndipo ife timaganiza kuti sitingathawe Mulungu padziko lapansi ndiponso sitingathawe pothamangitsidwa
  72,13,"‘Ndipo, ndithudi, pamene tidamva ulangizi wake, ife tidakhulupirira ndipo aliyense amene amakhulupirira mwa Ambuye wake sakhala ndi mantha otaya zake kapena kuponderezedwa"
  72,14,‘Ndipo pakati pathu pali ena amene amadzipereka kwathunthu kwa Mulungu ndi ena amene amachita zoipa. Iwo amene adzipereka kwa Mulungu amatsatira njira yoyenera.”
  72,15,Ndipo iwo amene amachita zoipa adzakhala nkhuni za ku Gahena
  72,16,"Ngati iwo akanakhulupirira ndi kutsatira njira yoyenera, Ife, ndithudi, tikadawapatsa mvula yambiri"
  72,17,Kuti tikhoza kuwayesa ndi izo. Ndi aliyense amene samvera chenjezo la Ambuye wake. Iye adzakonza kuti alandire chilango chowawa zedi
  72,18,Ndipo Mizikiti ndi ya Mulungu yekha. Motero musapembedze mulungu wina pambali pa Mulungu m’modzi yekha
  72,19,"Ndipo pamene kapolo wa Mulungu anaima kupempha kwa Iye, iwo adamuzungulira mu unyinji wawo mopanikizana"
  72,20,"Nena: “Ine ndimapempha kwa Ambuye wanga ndipo sindimufanizira Iye ndi wina aliyense.”"
  72,21,"Nena: “Ine ndilibe mphamvu yobweretsa pa inu chinthu choipa kapena kukubweretsani ku njira yoyenera.”"
  72,22,"Nena: “Palibe wina aliyense amene anganditeteze ine kwa Mulungu ndipo ine sindingapeze kothawira kwina kulikonse kupatula kwa Iye yekha.”"
  72,23,"“Udindo wanga ndi kukuuzani choonadi chimene ndalandira kuchokera kwa Mulungu ndi Uthenga wake, ndipo aliyense amene amanyoza Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake adzakhala ku moto wa ku Gahena nthawi zonse.”"
  72,24,"Mpaka pamene iwo ataona kuopsa kwa chilango chimene chidalonjezedwa kuti chidzafika pa iwo, pamenepo ndipo pamene adzadziwa mbali imene wopanda mphamvu ali ndipo kuti ndi ayani amene anali wochepa m’chiwerengero"
  72,25,"Nena: “Ine sindidziwa ngati chimene mwalonjezedwa chidzafika msanga kapena kuti Ambuye wangaadachiikapatali.”"
  72,26,Iyeyekhandiyeameneamadziwa zonse zobisika ndipo zinsinsi zake saululira wina aliyense ayi
  72,27,Kupatula kwa Atumwi ake amene Iye amawasankha yekha. Ndipo Iye amatumiza gulu la Atetezi amene amayenda patsogolo ndi pambuyo pawo
  72,28,Amawateteza mpaka pamene aona kuti iwo apereka uthenga wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo. Ndipo Iye amadziwa chili chonse chimene ali nacho ndipo Iye amasunga chiwerengero cha chinthu chili chonse